node.text:
Started the birthday month with a sumptuous breakfast that i think can last me all the way till dinner.

I had the Collin's Big Breakfast 🥞🍳🧀🥓($15.20 U.P $19) which consists of 2 Pancakes, Scrambled Eggs, Cheddar Cheese, Pork Bratwurst, Bacon Strips, Sautéed Mushrooms, Tater Tots, Salad and Coffee.

PROMO ✨ 20% off on their Breakfast Sets starting at just $12. Available on Delivery Apps and Takeaway from 7.30am to 10.30am.
Wow looks like a delish breakfast!!
Great breakfast to start the day 👍🏻
It's gonna be a great month ahead! 🤗🙆🏻‍♀️
That almost looks like the McDonald’s breakfast combo!
This looks like the perfect breakfast❤️
